    "title": "Strait of Hormuz reopens but UN warns poorest nations will face lasting economic fallout",
    "description": "NEW YORK CITY: The reopening of the Strait of Hormuz after more than 100 days of shipping disruption will bring relief to global energy and trade flows, but the world’s most vulnerable economies face a longer, costlier and more uneven path to recovery, the UN Conference on Trade and Development said in a new report.",
